OL,7,FJudge Roy Ellis said he has "never
OL,8,Fdealt with anywhere near the same
OL,9,Fextent of extraordinary devastation in
OL,10,Fa case."
OL,12,FThe judge said Button was under the
OL,13,Finfluence of the opioid-based
OL,14,Fpainkiller tramadol and had "abandoned
OL,15,Fhis responsibility" to keep all 35 of
OL,16,Fhis passengers safe.
OL,18,FEarlier in the day, Button made an
OL,19,Femotional statement, telling the court
OL,20,Fhe was "shamed of everything (he's)
OL,21,Fcaused".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
