OL,5,Cpeople dead
OL,7,F"I've tried to figure out the words to
OL,8,Fsay I'm sorry, but how do you say
OL,9,Fyou're sorry for such a horrible,
OL,10,Ftragic event that has ruined the lives
OL,11,Fof hundreds of people?" he said.
OL,13,F"I can't forgive myself, I can't
OL,14,Fbelieve I caused this, I never meant
OL,15,Fto cause it and I truly wish it never
OL,16,Fhappened.
OL,18,F"I live with this every day and I hate
OL,19,Fmyself I never meant to hurt anyone in
OL,20,Fmy entire life and now I've committed
OL,21,Fthe ultimate sin."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
