OL,7,FThere were cheers in the courtroom and
OL,8,Fcries of "yes" and "thank you" after
OL,9,Fthe sentence was handed down.
OL,11,FEarlier, victims' family members
OL,12,Fdelivered emotional victim impact
OL,13,Fstatements, telling the court of their
OL,14,Fgrief and trauma.
OL,16,FGraham McBride told how he awoke five
OL,17,Fdays after the crash in a hospital bed
OL,18,Fwith a fractured neck, ribs and arm
OL,19,Fand numerous cuts. He had lost his
OL,20,Fwife Nadene and only daughter Kyah in
OL,21,Fthe crash.
