OL,7,FThe court also heard that Button had
OL,8,Fbeen taking tramadol since the 1990s
OL,9,Fand had been stood down by a previous
OL,10,Femployer in 2022 after a pain
OL,11,Fspecialist ruled he was addicted to
OL,12,Fthe drug.
OL,14,FButton will be eligible for release on
OL,15,Fparole on May 7, 2048.
